+ * - fee=2 size=3 (feerate 0.667...)
+ * - fee=2 size=2 (feerate 1)
+ * - fee=1 size=1 (feerate 1)
+ * - fee=3 size=2 (feerate 1.5)
+ * - fee=2 size=1 (feerate 2)
+ * - fee=0 size=0 (undefined feerate)
